ol.li: Interrupt: PIC signals CPU, IDT dispatches handler
Acquisition: Handler reads scancode from port 0x60

Processing:
Check for 0xE0/0xE1 extended prefix
Check bit 7 for release vs press
Look up ASCII in scancode table
Buffer: Store KeyEvent in ring buffer

div.p: If 0xE0: Set extended flag Read next byte
If bit 7 set: Key released Clear from state
